<section xmlns:ns0="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>1-819.03</num>
  <heading>Issuance of regulations by Secretary.</heading>
  <text>The Secretary is authorized to issue regulations to implement, interpret, administer and carry out the purposes of this chapter, and, in the Secretary’s discretion, those regulations may have retroactive effect.</text>
